Hi I’m not new to all of this but I recently relapsed badly and I just don’t wanna feel alone with what I’m going thru and shit like that.. so I’m back on here. 
I’ll introduce myself, my name is June I’m 17 my Ed started when I was around 13/14.  I never really got help bc no one took it seriously.
My highest weight was around 71kg and my lowest 59.. ( I know it not that low.. but I’ve really struggled with binge eating and still do.) it’s a bad way of coping with stress and anxiety. 
If anyone wants to be friends or idk weightloss buddy’s dm me pls !
